  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:var(--space-2xl);align-items:flex-start">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px">
        <h2 style="margin-bottom:var(--space-md)">Check If We Service Your Area</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);margin-bottom:var(--space-lg);max-width:480px">Enter your ZIP code to confirm coverage. Currently serving 20 ZIP codes in Northwest Florida.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--text-secondary)"><strong>Cities:</strong> Pensacola, Gulf Breeze, Navarre, Milton, Pace, Cantonment</p>
